PrecisAmendments to the INCOME TAX REGULATIONS which give effect to amendments made to the Income Tax Act respecting the Tax on Large Corporations (Part I.3) and extend the tax on financial institutions to a number of prescribed corporations whose assets largely consist of shares in financial institutions or in its liabilities (Part VI).
